list.name: Releases
list.query: SELECT title, description from annotations WHERE $timeFilter order by time asc
list.rawQuery: select extract(epoch from time) AS time, title as text, description as tags from sannotations where $__timeFilter(time)

targets.rawSql:
with countries as (
  select unnest(string_to_array('${countries:csv}', ',')) as country
)
select
  s.time,
  [[columns]]
from
  sprjcntr s,
  countries c
where
  $__timeFilter(s.time)
  and s.period = '[[period]]'
  and s.series = 'prjcntr' || c.country || '[[metric]]'
group by
  s.time
order by
  s.time
